name: Michael S. Hansen on GitHub
tagline: Michael S. Hansen's Collection of Stuff on GitHub
body:
### Welcome 

This page is really just a place holder for various projects I am involved in.

If you are looking for the ISMRM sunrise course notes and code, go to http://hansenms.github.io/sunrise.

The gadgetron can be found at http://gadgetron.github.io

ISMRM Raw Data format (ISMRMRD) can be found at http://ismrmrd.github.io
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
